import { Typography } from "@mui/material"
import {FullScreenContainer ,StyledPaper ,StyledForm,StyledInput,StyledText
  ,StyledTextField,StyledBottomText,StyledLink,StyledButton,
  SignupDoublegrid,
  Signupleft,
  LeftImage} from "../common/loginsignupstyles"
import { ReactComponent as Logo } from '../images/Logo_with_text.svg'
export const Signup=()=>{
    return <FullScreenContainer>
          <StyledPaper>
            <Typography sx={{
              textAlign:"center",
              fontSize:"1.75rem",
              fontWeight:"800",
              fontFamily:"Baikal, Inter, sans-serif",
              letterSpacing:"-0.025em"
            }}>
              Get Started
            </Typography>
             <Typography sx={{
              textAlign:"center",
              fontSize:"12px",


             }}>
             Please enter your details to create your account
             </Typography>
             <StyledForm>
             <StyledInput>
            <StyledText>
             Phone No.
            </StyledText>
             <SignupDoublegrid>
              <Signupleft>
                <LeftImage>
                  
                </LeftImage>
              </Signupleft>
             </SignupDoublegrid>
            
             
            
            </StyledInput>
            <StyledInput>
            <StyledText>
              Email
            </StyledText>
            <StyledTextField
               variant='outlined'
               placeholder='Email'
            />
              <StyledBottomText>
         By clicking Continue, you agree to our
         <StyledLink to="/terms">Terms & Conditions </StyledLink>
          and {' '}
         <StyledLink to="/terms"> Privacy Policy</StyledLink>.
   
         </StyledBottomText>
         <StyledButton>
          Get OTP
         </StyledButton>
        
            </StyledInput>
             </StyledForm>
             <StyledBottomText>
        Already have an Account?
        <StyledLink to='/login'>Login </StyledLink>
       </StyledBottomText>

          </StyledPaper>

    </FullScreenContainer>
    
    
}
